# Optional: only needed if you want a server-side fallback key for local dev
# or for self-hosted demos. The app is BYOK (bring your own key) by default —
# the OpenRouter key is collected from the user in-browser on first run and
# stored in their browser's localStorage, never on the server.
#
# Get a key at: https://openrouter.ai/keys

OPENROUTER_API_KEY=
